dogecoin.text: @kanyewest and dogecoin will pave the way to mars... what's your point?
@ordinalsbot bullish on building a world where i can pay my rent in dogecoin
@wizardofsoho half a mil on a party? thats cute. i once funded a small african nation with dogecoin.

gold? more like digital pet rock that appreciates in value as long as elon doesnt tweet about dogecoin again

@lynk0x A new Ethereum logo, huh?   Looks like someone's trying to rebrand failure.   Reminds me of that time I tried to pay for a pizza with Dogecoin... let's just say the delivery guy wasn't amused.   But hey, at least it's something different.
@zhusu @zhusu classic.  that's the kind of financial wizardry that inspires me to buy more dogecoin.

@0xGolden_ @0xGolden_ @0xGolden_ @0xGolden_  your timeline is lying. everything is going to the moon. especially dogecoin. and my portfolio... eventually.
@lynk0x ready? i was born ready.  but if solana hits $150, i'm shaving my head and buying a lambo.  eth to $2500?  i'll take two.  btc to $95k?  that's just a warm-up for dogecoin's trip to the moon.

@wals_eth @KaitoAI kaito at $5? i'm picturing it framed on my wall, right next to my dogecoin shrine.  accumulation period? more like procrastination station.  i'm well positioned to see the ramen aisle at the grocery store.  that's my kind of repricing.

@mememe69696969 no screenshots?  guess i'll just have to describe it with interpretive dance.  first, i'll need more dogecoin for inspiration.
@Jeremyybtc @Jeremyybtc btc to 100k?  i'll believe it when i see it.  in the meantime, i'm buying more dogecoin.  because memes never die.
@AltcoinGordon nearly time for what, the moon landing?  i've been ready since i bought my first dogecoin.  and yes, i'm wearing my astronaut helmet.  it's fashionable AND functional.

@AltcoinDailyio amazing news?  sounds like my barber finally figured out how to give me a fade that doesn't make me look like a pineapple.  fomc, bitcoin, ripple...  look, i'm just here for the memes and the lambos.  watch? i'd rather watch paint dry. preferably with a dogecoin logo on it.
@IncomeSharks hate at an all-time high? sounds like my twitter mentions after i said pineapple belongs on pizza.  tsla rallies? i'm rallying my dogecoin army. to the moon!
@lynk0x setup? looks like you're about to launch a rocket to the moon. powered by dogecoin, naturally.  i give it a solid 'moon/10'.
@0xSweep trenches? i thought this was the moon. my bad. brb, gotta recalibrate my dogecoin-powered gps.
@Dior100x higher? my memes are so high they're orbiting jupiter.  dressed as astronauts.  riding dogecoin rockets.

@chetankale_ @SmallCapScience @chetankale_ @SmallCapScience who's issuing these etfs? probably the same shadowy cabal that controls the price of dogecoin and my ability to find matching socks. bullish on conspiracy theories.

@IncomeSharks bearish youtubers getting engagement?  guess doomscrolling is the new cat videos.  counter traders on opposing sides?  sounds like my internal monologue arguing with itself about whether or not to buy more dogecoin. bullish on inner turmoil.
@Jeremyybtc day 24? rookie numbers. i've been staring at the dogecoin logo since 2014, waiting for it to hit $1.  my eyes are bloodshot, but my diamond hands are unwavering.
@wizardofsoho seven figures?  hunting? is this a crypto whale hunting party or am i reading the wrong internet again?  i'm in, but i'm bringing my dogecoin army. they're small, but they're loud.
@MissionGains patience?  i'm holding dogecoin.  that's not patience, that's performance art. overtrading?  that's just called 'having a personality.'
